## ğŸ“‹ Overview

**Brain Tumor Detector & Classifier** is a sophisticated yet user-friendly web application that leverages **deep learning** to classify brain MRI scans into four distinct categories:

| Category | Icon | Description |
|----------|------|-------------|
| **Glioma Tumor** | ğŸ”´ | Tumors originating from glial cells |
| **Meningioma Tumor** | ğŸŸ£ | Tumors from the brain membranes |
| **Pituitary Tumor** | ğŸŸ¡ | Tumors in the pituitary gland |
| **No Tumor** | ğŸŸ¢ | Normal brain scan |

**Built with:** Python â€¢ Flask â€¢ TensorFlow/Keras â€¢ OpenCV  
**Model:** VGG16 Transfer Learning (150Ã—150 input size)  
**Status:** Educational & Research Use Only

