## ğŸš€ Advanced Usage

### Retrain the Model
```bash
# Open Jupyter notebook and run all cells
jupyter notebook training/Brain_Tumor_Training.ipynb
```

### Run in Production
```bash
# Install production WSGI server
pip install gunicorn

# Run app
gunicorn -w 4 -b 0.0.0.0:5000 app:app
```

### API Request Example
```bash
# Upload image and get prediction
curl -X POST -F "file=@scan.jpg" http://127.0.0.1:5000/predict
```

